I love that smell.
Ocean air.

00:00:41.942 --> 00:00:44.044
'Professor Sycamore.'
[EXCITED]

00:00:44.044 --> 00:00:46.146
‐ Hi, hi.
‐ Long time no see.

00:00:46.146 --> 00:00:47.881
Hi, there.

00:00:47.881 --> 00:00:49.883
It was so nice of you
to invite us.

