The Twerps
did make the scene.

00:01:47.174 --> 00:01:49.309
We hit that on the head.

00:01:49.309 --> 00:01:51.812
With the professor as host,
their appearance was a must.

00:01:51.812 --> 00:01:53.280
Let's take it slow.

00:01:53.280 --> 00:01:55.315
And at the right time

00:01:55.315 --> 00:01:57.951
we'll whisk all their Pokémon
away in one fell swoop.

00:01:57.951 --> 00:01:59.953
Working to earn
everyone's trust is a must.

00:01:59.953 --> 00:02:03.657
[gasps]

00:02:03.657 --> 00:02:06.259
Madame Catherine,
you're right on time.

00:02:06.259 --> 00:02:09.329
We're just gettin' our gourmet
preparations underway now.

00:02:09.329 --> 00:02:11.565
Good. No skimping, please.

00:02:11.565 --> 00:02:13.634
Keep in mind
Augustine's Trainers

00:02:13.634 --> 00:02:15.936
have giant appetites
and just love to eat.

00:02:15.936 --> 00:02:18.839
Prepare a ton of food
at least.

00:02:18.839 --> 00:02:20.140
JESSIE/JAMES/MEOWTH
Yes, ma'am.

00:02:20.140 --> 00:02:22.542
And if they really like
what you all cook

00:02:22.542 --> 00:02:24.911
there might just be a little
raise in store.

00:02:24.911 --> 00:02:27.214
[all gasp]
Yummy.

