‐ And that's what happened.
‐ Hm.

00:02:31.752 --> 00:02:35.055
Wow! Great!
What a marvelous experience.

00:02:35.055 --> 00:02:37.391
You met Mega Lucario?

00:02:37.391 --> 00:02:40.127
Mega Evolution
is as cool as it gets.

00:02:40.127 --> 00:02:42.062
Everything powers up

00:02:42.062 --> 00:02:43.730
including the strength
of their moves.

00:02:43.730 --> 00:02:45.499
It's awesome
how strong they get.

00:02:45.499 --> 00:02:47.701
I wish I could've
seen it too.

00:02:47.701 --> 00:02:50.737
So I guess you'll be
battling Korrina

00:02:50.737 --> 00:02:53.807
and that powerful Mega Lucario
at the Shalour Gym soon.

00:02:53.807 --> 00:02:55.909
You bet.
The stronger my opponent is

00:02:55.909 --> 00:02:58.045
the more fired up I get.

00:02:58.045 --> 00:02:59.513
I'm gonna win that Gym badge
for sure.

00:02:59.513 --> 00:03:01.515
[DETERMINED]

00:03:01.515 --> 00:03:03.417
Well, I hope
your stay here will be useful

00:03:03.417 --> 00:03:04.718
and marvelous
at the same time.

00:03:04.718 --> 00:03:05.585
ASH
Thanks.

00:03:08.355 --> 00:03:10.424
This is the cabin
you'll be staying in.

00:03:10.424 --> 00:03:14.061
Wow. It's the cutest.

00:03:14.061 --> 00:03:16.096
'Everyone will be
split into teams.'

00:03:16.096 --> 00:03:18.732
'As you can see, your team
is called Team Froakie.'

00:03:18.732 --> 00:03:20.300
Team Froakie, huh?
Cool.

00:03:23.603 --> 00:03:26.540
‐ Ha..
‐ Ha‐ha‐ha.

00:03:26.540 --> 00:03:28.075
Hey, I call this bed.

00:03:28.075 --> 00:03:29.142
[AGREEMENT]

00:03:33.914 --> 00:03:36.049
Speaking of summer camp

00:03:36.049 --> 00:03:37.818
'does this bring back
any memories'

00:03:37.818 --> 00:03:40.153
'of when you two
first met each other?'

00:03:40.153 --> 00:03:42.055
‐ Yeah, it does.
‐ Huh?

00:03:42.055 --> 00:03:43.924
Let's make it as much fun
as when we were kids.

00:03:43.924 --> 00:03:45.726
‐ It's a deal.
‐ 'Alright.'

00:03:45.726 --> 00:03:46.626
‐ Huh?
‐ 'Battle begin!'

00:03:46.626 --> 00:03:48.695
[FOCUSED

00:03:48.695 --> 00:03:50.931
Hey, it's a Squirtle!

00:03:50.931 --> 00:03:51.932
Huh.

00:03:54.801 --> 00:03:57.637
Squirtle.
The Tiny Turtle Pokémon.

00:03:57.637 --> 00:03:59.773
'During battle,
Squirtle hides in its shell'

00:03:59.773 --> 00:04:01.108
'that sprays water
at its opponent'

00:04:01.108 --> 00:04:02.509
'whenever it can.'

00:04:02.509 --> 00:04:04.845
Conkeldurr, Superpower!

00:04:04.845 --> 00:04:06.613
[SUPERPOWER MOVE]

