Quick, Squirtle.
Dodge by gettin' in close.

00:04:08.782 --> 00:04:10.650
[SUPERPOWER MOVE]

00:04:10.650 --> 00:04:13.086
[EXERTION]

00:04:13.086 --> 00:04:15.655
‐ Whoa, it jumped.
‐ Yeah. And it jumped high.

00:04:15.655 --> 00:04:17.023
[EXERTION]

00:04:20.360 --> 00:04:22.863
[ANNOYED]

00:04:22.863 --> 00:04:25.565
‐ Hey! Stop moving.
‐ But it's what we do.

00:04:25.565 --> 00:04:27.734
We just can't
stand still, see?

00:04:27.734 --> 00:04:30.537
[HAPPY]

00:04:30.537 --> 00:04:32.272
SERENA
'It's as if they're dancing.'

00:04:32.272 --> 00:04:34.875
That Squirtle's somethin' else.
[AMAZED]

00:04:34.875 --> 00:04:37.043
It's having lots of fun
battling.

00:04:37.043 --> 00:04:39.346
'You're right.
Look at that smile.'

00:04:39.346 --> 00:04:41.114
Now, Skull Bash.

00:04:41.114 --> 00:04:42.716
[SKULL BASH MOVE]

00:04:42.716 --> 00:04:45.085
[PAINED]

00:04:46.453 --> 00:04:48.855
[DAZED]

00:04:48.855 --> 00:04:51.158
‐ Conkeldurr.
‐ We nailed that one.

00:04:51.158 --> 00:04:52.292
Squirtle wins it.

00:04:52.292 --> 00:04:53.660
[EXERTION]

00:04:53.660 --> 00:04:55.796
[PROUD]

00:04:55.796 --> 00:04:57.497
‐ Great job!
‐ Really awesome!

00:04:57.497 --> 00:05:01.067
Thanks, Conkeldurr.
Good job.

00:05:01.067 --> 00:05:03.837
Boy, oh, boy. Your battle style
is a first for me.

00:05:03.837 --> 00:05:05.772
We love to dance. We just keep
on movin' and groovin'.

00:05:05.772 --> 00:05:07.574
[HAPPY]

00:05:07.574 --> 00:05:09.576
Hey. Can I battle
with you next?

00:05:09.576 --> 00:05:10.944
[EXCITED]

00:05:10.944 --> 00:05:12.913
Alright. Sounds great.

00:05:12.913 --> 00:05:15.448
I'm Tierno
and I'm from Santelune City.

00:05:15.448 --> 00:05:16.883
And Squirtle here
is my partner.

00:05:16.883 --> 00:05:18.852
[SALUTATIONS]

00:05:18.852 --> 00:05:21.521
We're part of Team Squirtle.
What about you guys?

00:05:21.521 --> 00:05:23.857
All of us are part
of Team Froakie.

00:05:23.857 --> 00:05:26.026
I'm Ash Ketchum.
I'm from Pallet Town.

00:05:26.026 --> 00:05:27.561
My partner's Pikachu.

00:05:27.561 --> 00:05:29.329
[SALUTATIONS]

00:05:29.329 --> 00:05:31.164
‐ Pallet Town?
‐ That's right.

00:05:31.164 --> 00:05:33.266
See, I'm from Kanto,
but I came here

00:05:33.266 --> 00:05:34.501
so I can enter
the Kalos League.

00:05:34.501 --> 00:05:35.669
TIERNO
'Some haul.

00:05:35.669 --> 00:05:37.704
All the way from Kanto, huh?'

00:05:37.704 --> 00:05:39.739
Hold on.
I know you.

00:05:39.739 --> 00:05:42.075
Huh? Wait. You do?

00:05:42.075 --> 00:05:43.977
‐ Yeah. Stay here.
‐ Now what?

00:05:43.977 --> 00:05:45.011
[CONFUSED]

00:05:48.148 --> 00:05:50.450
Look. Check it out.
She looks the same.

00:05:50.450 --> 00:05:54.421
It's you. This is great.
You're Serena.

00:05:54.421 --> 00:05:57.023
But how could you
know my name?

00:05:57.023 --> 00:05:58.625
Because I saw you
on Pokévision.

00:05:58.625 --> 00:05:59.526
Huh?

00:06:03.263 --> 00:06:05.699
Wait. Isn't Pokévision..

00:06:05.699 --> 00:06:08.201
[CONFUSED]
Yep. Remember Serena's video?

00:06:08.201 --> 00:06:10.403
Ah! Ah! Oh.

00:06:10.403 --> 00:06:12.772
CLEMONT
Oh, no. That means people

00:06:12.772 --> 00:06:15.175
are watching me too?

00:06:15.175 --> 00:06:17.811
Of course, they are. Come on,
that's the whole point, silly.

00:06:17.811 --> 00:06:19.813
[laughing]

00:06:19.813 --> 00:06:23.650
‐ I'm Shauna. Nice to meet you.
‐ Shauna. Thank you.

00:06:23.650 --> 00:06:25.819
You and Fennekin
are so cute in your video

00:06:25.819 --> 00:06:28.421
that I've been a fan
ever since I first saw it.

00:06:28.421 --> 00:06:31.591
‐ Oh, wow. Thanks.
‐ Where'd you see the video?

00:06:31.591 --> 00:06:34.561
Where? At the Pokémon Center.
You can watch it anywhere.

00:06:34.561 --> 00:06:35.896
You haven't seen
your video yet?

00:06:35.896 --> 00:06:36.930
Uh..

00:06:42.736 --> 00:06:45.105
Your Squirtle is just fine
and back to perfect health.

00:06:45.105 --> 00:06:47.440
Thanks, Nurse Joy.
[HAPPY]

00:06:47.440 --> 00:06:48.808
I'm glad
you're feelin' good, kiddo.

00:06:52.045 --> 00:06:54.447
Whenever I visit
the Pokémon Center

00:06:54.447 --> 00:06:57.217
I always check if something
is new on Pokévision.

00:06:57.217 --> 00:06:58.985
'See? This one's Serena's.'

00:06:58.985 --> 00:07:01.521
Look how many views
it's gotten.

00:07:01.521 --> 00:07:04.457
That's great. I had no idea
they were watching.

00:07:04.457 --> 00:07:06.626
Can I meet your Fennekin,
please?

00:07:06.626 --> 00:07:09.763
Sure. No problem.
Fennekin, come on out!

00:07:09.763 --> 00:07:11.331
[APPEARING]

00:07:11.331 --> 00:07:12.933
[HAPPY]

00:07:12.933 --> 00:07:15.735
So cute. You're too cute.

00:07:15.735 --> 00:07:17.637
Fennekin's even cuter
in person.

00:07:17.637 --> 00:07:20.073
Thank you, Shauna.

00:07:20.073 --> 00:07:22.542
Grooming its tail
must be lots of work

00:07:22.542 --> 00:07:24.444
but it's totally shiny
and smooth.

00:07:24.444 --> 00:07:26.112
That's so sweet.

00:07:26.112 --> 00:07:28.281
It's because I brush it
all the time.

00:07:28.281 --> 00:07:30.350
Do you make
Pokévision videos too?

00:07:30.350 --> 00:07:32.152
Sure do.
I've made a whole bunch.

00:07:34.054 --> 00:07:36.189
'Whoa. That's a lot.'

00:07:36.189 --> 00:07:38.792
I always make one
when I catch a new Pokémon.

00:07:38.792 --> 00:07:40.627
I even make a new video
every time

00:07:40.627 --> 00:07:42.762
I manage to get my hands
on a pretty new ribbon.

00:07:45.532 --> 00:07:47.667
[SALUTATIONS]

00:07:47.667 --> 00:07:50.337
Time for Shauna's Pokémon Show.

00:07:50.337 --> 00:07:53.373
My partner for today
is Bulbasaur.

00:07:53.373 --> 00:07:54.975
It's super cute
when it runs.

00:07:54.975 --> 00:07:56.509
And even with
its short legs

00:07:56.509 --> 00:07:58.445
Bulbasaur's really good
at running.

00:07:58.445 --> 00:08:00.180
It was my very
first Pokémon.

00:08:00.180 --> 00:08:02.082
[HAPPY]

00:08:02.082 --> 00:08:03.783
Everybody's favorite.

00:08:03.783 --> 00:08:05.652
[HAPPY]

00:08:05.652 --> 00:08:07.120
It has a super‐cute
voice too.

00:08:07.120 --> 00:08:09.122
[VINE WHIP MOVE]

00:08:09.122 --> 00:08:11.257
Can't wait to see
what will bloom from its seed.

00:08:11.257 --> 00:08:13.226
I hope that
you're all excited too.

00:08:17.197 --> 00:08:19.699
‐ Well, there it is.
‐ You've got a Bulbasaur.

00:08:19.699 --> 00:08:21.968
Yep. It's my go‐to
Pokémon pal.

00:08:21.968 --> 00:08:24.070
Bulbasaur, come out!

00:08:24.070 --> 00:08:26.339
[APPEARING]

00:08:26.339 --> 00:08:28.475
[READY]

00:08:28.475 --> 00:08:30.010
Just like in the video.

00:08:32.312 --> 00:08:34.848
Bulbasaur. The Seed Pokémon.

00:08:34.848 --> 00:08:37.217
'A young Bulbasaur uses
the nutrients from its seed'

00:08:37.217 --> 00:08:39.519
'for the energy
it needs to grow.'

00:08:39.519 --> 00:08:41.521
Don't you think
Bulbasaur's super‐cute too?

00:08:41.521 --> 00:08:44.424
Sure do.
[SALUTATIONS]

00:08:45.859 --> 00:08:49.062
[SALUTATIONS]

00:08:49.062 --> 00:08:52.165
[UNINTERESTED]
[CONFUSED]

00:08:52.165 --> 00:08:54.401
I guess your Bulbasaur
is kind of snooty, huh?

00:08:54.401 --> 00:08:55.735
‐ 'Yeah.'
‐ Huh?

00:08:55.735 --> 00:08:57.637
[APPEARING]

00:08:57.637 --> 00:09:00.073
Huh? Chespin.

00:09:00.073 --> 00:09:01.641
I think Chespin
wants to play.

00:09:01.641 --> 00:09:03.109
Froakie, come on out!

00:09:03.109 --> 00:09:05.078
[APPEARING]

00:09:05.078 --> 00:09:06.846
[SALUTATIONS]

00:09:08.481 --> 00:09:09.482
‐ Oh, yeah!
‐ Huh?

00:09:11.317 --> 00:09:14.020
‐ Ta‐da!
‐ Poké Puffs?

00:09:14.020 --> 00:09:16.756
‐ Did you bake these, Serena?
‐ Mm‐hm.

00:09:16.756 --> 00:09:19.092
Here. I hope
you all like them.

00:09:19.092 --> 00:09:20.460
For you.

00:09:20.460 --> 00:09:22.529
[CONTENT]

00:09:24.030 --> 00:09:25.398
'Well?'

00:09:25.398 --> 00:09:26.666
[HAPPY]

00:09:26.666 --> 00:09:28.501
[CONTENT]

00:09:30.303 --> 00:09:31.971
Bulbasaur?
One for you.

00:09:31.971 --> 00:09:33.573
Huh?

00:09:34.507 --> 00:09:36.643
Sorry.

00:09:36.643 --> 00:09:38.978
Because my Bulbasaur's
a teensy bit shy around others

00:09:38.978 --> 00:09:41.114
it won't eat anything
unless I feed it.

00:09:41.114 --> 00:09:42.082
‐ Then go right ahead.
‐ Thanks.

00:09:44.284 --> 00:09:45.618
Here. It's for you.

00:09:47.120 --> 00:09:49.622
[UNSURE] / [CONTENT]

00:09:52.459 --> 00:09:56.096
‐ 'Huh? Was that a smile?'
‐ Bulbasaur really loves it.

00:09:56.096 --> 00:09:58.465
But that's the most emotion
you'll ever see.

00:09:58.465 --> 00:10:00.266
I'm so glad
you like my Poké Puffs.

00:10:00.266 --> 00:10:01.935
[EXERTION]

00:10:03.269 --> 00:10:04.771
[SHOCK]

00:10:04.771 --> 00:10:07.140
[SHOCK]
Wow! Charmander!

