You never know
what Ash is going to do.

00:19:03.609 --> 00:19:05.344
I'm always learning
new things to do

00:19:05.344 --> 00:19:06.779
for Pokémon
through his actions.

00:19:06.779 --> 00:19:08.914
You're never sure
of what's next.

00:19:08.914 --> 00:19:12.251
Oh, man, come on.
It's not such a big deal.

00:19:12.251 --> 00:19:13.786
But your inventions
are totally amazing.

00:19:13.786 --> 00:19:15.655
An inventor?

00:19:15.655 --> 00:19:17.289
His inventions are always
helping us out.

00:19:19.091 --> 00:19:20.860
‐ Here.
‐ Huh.

00:19:20.860 --> 00:19:22.461
Whoa! What's that?

00:19:22.461 --> 00:19:24.430
Inventing is my passion.

00:19:24.430 --> 00:19:26.098
I love coming up with things

00:19:26.098 --> 00:19:27.833
that benefit the lives
of Pokémon.

00:19:27.833 --> 00:19:29.869
My brother's inventions
are unbelievable.

00:19:29.869 --> 00:19:33.773
Awesome. That's so cool.

00:19:33.773 --> 00:19:36.208
Serena, how did your battle
against Shauna go?

00:19:36.208 --> 00:19:38.010
It was a lot of fun.

00:19:38.010 --> 00:19:40.413
I figured out
a lot of things.

00:19:40.413 --> 00:19:42.314
'Shauna showed me
a lot of things too.'

00:19:42.314 --> 00:19:43.349
[laughing]

00:19:47.453 --> 00:19:49.188
They seem
to enjoy our cuisine.

00:19:49.188 --> 00:19:51.757
It's all because
of your recipes.

00:19:51.757 --> 00:19:54.160
It's all because
I'm the official taste‐tester.

00:19:54.160 --> 00:19:55.461
Wait. You can't brag
about that.

