[AGREEMENT]

00:19:58.764 --> 00:19:59.865
[gasps]

00:20:02.768 --> 00:20:04.870
You've done a great job.

00:20:04.870 --> 00:20:06.439
The kids just
adore your cooking.

00:20:06.439 --> 00:20:08.207
Raise time!

00:20:08.207 --> 00:20:09.608
JESSIE/JAMES/MEOWTH
Ah. Thanks!

00:20:19.418 --> 00:20:21.454
Becoming a Pokémon Master.

00:20:21.454 --> 00:20:22.922
[CONFUSED]

00:20:22.922 --> 00:20:25.357
Ash isn't the only one.

00:20:25.357 --> 00:20:29.295
'There's Clemont, Shauna,
Tierno and Trevor.'

