They're all on a journey
to make their dreams come true.

00:20:31.363 --> 00:20:32.932
[CONTENT]

00:20:35.134 --> 00:20:37.269
But I need a dream too.

00:20:40.039 --> 00:20:41.841
NARRATOR
Day one of Professor Sycamore's

00:20:41.841 --> 00:20:44.777
Pokémon summer camp
is almost at an end.

00:20:44.777 --> 00:20:46.245
With so many new friends
and experiences

00:20:46.245 --> 00:20:47.446
to reflect upon

00:20:47.446 --> 00:20:49.415
only time will tell

00:20:49.415 --> 00:20:50.850
if it will affect
our heroes

00:20:50.850 --> 00:20:53.018
as the journey continues.

